snippet.title: Neutron C64
snippet.description:
"Neutron" is a new vertically scrolling SHMUP by Witchsoft for the Commodore 64, an entry for the RGCD C64 16KB GameDev Compo 2019.

Code, graphics and music: Sarah Jane Avory.

Follow my progress on my other C64 projects on Twitter: https://twitter.com/SarahJaneAvory
